Install Base Targeting: A Use Case Where AI Truly Shines
Install base targeting — identifying companies already using complementary or competing technologies and reaching them with highly relevant messaging — has always been a sophisticated but powerful demand generation strategy. In 2026, ChatGPT and AI-driven tools have made this strategy more accessible and more precise than ever before.

How does AI enhance install base targeting? The answer lies in data synthesis. ChatGPT can process large volumes of technographic data, company signals, and behavioral intent data to identify which accounts in a target market are actively evaluating new solutions, dissatisfied with their current vendors, or approaching contract renewal windows. This intelligence, combined with AI-generated personalized outreach, creates a demand generation engine that targets buyers at the exact moment they are most receptive.

For technology companies in particular — whether in cybersecurity, data management, HR tech, or enterprise software — install base targeting powered by AI has become one of the highest-ROI strategies available in 2026.

